	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "seller-products-api-001",
		"name": "Seller Products API",
		"description": "Complete Seller Product Management APIs - Phase 2 Frontend Compatible\n\n**Features:**\n- Product CRUD operations for sellers\n- Image upload (main, product images, variant images)\n- Product variants management\n- Auto-approval enabled for products\n- Category-based attributes\n\n**Authentication:** Required (SELLER role)\n\n**Base URL:** {{base_url}}/api/seller/products",
